{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "12", "m": "05", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "22", "M": "51", "S": "04"}}, "news": [{"title": "NCLT allows withdrawal of insolvency proceedings against Nobility Estates", "para": "The NCLT has allowed withdrawal of insolvency proceedings against Nobility Estates, developer of ATS Group\u2019s Le Grandiose project in Noida, after lenders and the erstwhile management reached a settlement. The tribunal noted that the withdrawal proposal received 92.52% approval from the committee of creditors, including votes from 636 homebuyers, and directed restoration of management control to the company\u2019s board.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/nclt-approves-withdrawal-of-insolvency-proceedings-for-nobility-estates-after-key-settlement/131039740?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-82066/131039740.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}, {"title": "India's USD 1.5-billion proptech market is booming - but almost no one is making money", "para": "A deep-dive brokerage report reveals a sector caught in a structural bind: residential real estate transactions have hit record highs, yet the digital platforms riding that boom, from listing portals to transaction brokers to home interior firms, are burning cash, losing the advertising war to Google and Meta, and scrambling to reinvent themselves by piling into each other's businesses. ", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/allied-industries/indias-proptech-market-booming-sales-yet-struggling-for-profitability/131037742?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-36442/131037742.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "allied-industries"}, {"title": "Berger Paints' net profit declines 4.63% to \u20b91,128.02 crore in FY26", "para": "Berger Paints saw its net p